author: Source: Lethbridge Herald
title: Tucker makes 52-yard FG in overtime, Ravens beat Steelers 23-20 for first win... - Lethbridge Herald
text:
The big-legged Baltimore kicker hit a 42-yard field goal to tie the Pittsburgh Steelers in the final seconds of regulation and made a 52-yarder with 5:08 left in overtime to give the Ravens a 23-20 victory Thursday night. Scobee had two chances to give the Steelers some cushion late in the fourth quarter only to pull both kicks wide left.
 Lethbridge Herald.
